trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultAttributeCollection" /> class is a collection of <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryAttribute" /> objects.
The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultAttributeCollection.AttributeNames" /> property contains names of attributes in this collection.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultAttributeCollection.AttributeNames" /> 속성에는 이 컬렉션의 특성 이름이 포함되어 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: Names of attributes in this collection.
The name of the attribute to locate.

The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultAttributeCollection.Contains(System.String)" /> method determines whether the collection contains the specified <paramref name="attributeName" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultAttributeCollection.Contains(System.String)" /> 메서드는 컬렉션에 지정된 <paramref name="attributeName" />이 포함되어 있는지 여부를 확인합니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the collection contains attributeName or <see langword="false" /> if it does not.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션에 attributeName이 포함되어 있으면 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="attributeName" /> is a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="attributeName" />이 null 참조(Visual Basic의 경우 <see langword="Nothing" />)인 경우

trans-unit.source: A one-dimensional array that is the destination of the elements copied from the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultAttributeCollection" /> object.
The zero-based index of <c>array</c> where copying begins.

The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultAttributeCollection.CopyTo(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryAttribute[],System.Int32)" /> method copies the entire collection to a one-dimensional array, starting at the specified index of the target array.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultAttributeCollection.CopyTo(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryAttribute[],System.Int32)" /> 메서드는 대상 배열의 지정된 인덱스에서 시작하여 1차원 배열에 전체 컬렉션을 복사합니다.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="array" /> is a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="array" />이 null 참조(Visual Basic의 경우 <see langword="Nothing" />)인 경우

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="index" /> is less than zero.
<paramref name="array" /> is multidimensional
-or-

The number of elements in the source <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultAttributeCollection" /> is greater than the available space from <paramref name="index" /> to the end of the destination <paramref name="array" />.
trans-unit.target: 소스 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultAttributeCollection" />의 요소 수가 대상 <paramref name="array" />의 <paramref name="index" />부터 끝까지 사용 가능한 공간보다 큽니다.

trans-unit.source: The type of the source <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultAttributeCollection" /> cannot be cast automatically to the type of the destination <paramref name="array" />.
trans-unit.target: 소스 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultAttributeCollection" />의 형식을 대상 <paramref name="array" />의 형식으로 자동 캐스팅할 수 없습니다.

trans-unit.source: The name of this attribute.

The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultAttributeCollection.Item(System.String)" /> property contains the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryAttribute" /> object specified by <paramref name="attributeName" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultAttributeCollection.Item(System.String)" /> 속성에는 <paramref name="attributeName" />으로 지정된 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryAttribute" /> 개체가 포함되어 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryAttribute" /> object specified by <paramref name="attributeName" />.
The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultAttributeCollection.Values" /> property contains values of attributes in this collection.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultAttributeCollection.Values" /> 속성에는 이 컬렉션의 특성 값이 포함되어 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: Values of attributes in this collection.
